ash of, well, so many aspects of his dervish=E2=80=94the reversed O.M.B. fr=
eeze, the elongated nomination battle royales, and the attendant anxieties =
and animosities of both his supplicants and foes on Capitol Hill. If you re=
ally want a flavor of what=E2=80=99s going on in the nation=E2=80=99s capit=
al, I=E2=80=99d suggest devouring Leigh Ann=E2=80=99s two masterstrokes,
